Python Scripts For CWA tables
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Before running any of these MySQL must be installed on the machine
To get mysql type:
1)sudo apt-get install mysql-server
2)type yes(Y) for the download
3)set up a root password

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FILES INCLUDED (TO RUN type "python _fileName_" then type mysql db password)
createDB.py  -creates the cwa database using dictionary in tableSQL.py
deleteDB.py  -will delete the cwa database removing all entrys and tables
tableSQL.py  -python dictionary containing SQL for creating DB
show_tablesDB.py -will show all tables in the database

#In createDB, deleteDB and show_tables comment out "password = getpass.getpass()" with #
#Then replace passwd in cnx ='your password'
#This way you don't have to always enter your password to use the files

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To enter mysql db from the machine:
1)Enter: mysql -u root -p
2)enter your password
3)Run sql commands

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Basic Commands
SHOW DATABSES; -shows all databaes in root(there will be a few default ones)
USE _dbName_;  -switch to and work in the dbName given

SHOW TABLES
SHOW COLUMNS FROM _tableName_; -List all feilds in tableName and show their values
CREATE TABLE _tableNAME (varibale1 type1, variable2, type2....) -create a table with given variables
DROP _tableName_ -remove a table from the database

SELECT * FROM _tableName_; -show all(-) entrys in the tableName
SELECT_feild_ FROM _tableName_ WHERE _feild2_ _comparison_ -show all feilds where a specific conditon is met eg. SELECT name FROM users WHERE age > 5;

INSERT INTO _tableName_(feild1,feild2...) VALUES(value1,value2...); -Insert in to the tableName
DELETE FROM _tableName_ _feild_ WHERE _condition_ -Delete all entrys in tableName where condtion is met


